  |                                                                         |
  |     Summary                                                             |
  |   -------------------------------------------------------------------   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Step into a career as a pro-racer, mastering the world's fastest      |
  |   cars to win motorsport's most exciting races, from the hallowed       |
  |   asphalt of the Indianapolis Motor Speedway to the narrow city         |
  |   streets of Barcelona.                                                 |
  |                                                                         |
  |   RACE ANYTIME, ANYWHERE.                                               |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Enjoy best-in-class AAA racing at home or on the move!                |
  |                                                                         |
  |   SCALEABLE CHALLENGE.                                                  |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Customize your controls and difficulty level. From nice 'n easy to    |
  |   super hard, it's up to you to set the bar.                            |
  |                                                                         |
  |   MASTER FIVE DIFFERENT RACING DISCIPLINES.                             |
  |                                                                         |
  |   CARS AND CIRCUITS.                                                    |
  |                                                                         |
  |   From the McLAREN 12C GT3 to the MAZDA RX-7 (FD3S) DRIFT TUNED,        |
  |   unleash Muscle Cars, Super Modified motors, Hypercars, Hot Hatches    |
  |   and a huge range of other high-performance rides across a ton of      |
  |   tracks, roads, laps and loops.                                        |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Touring: Take on aggressive pack races                              |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Endurance: Test your strength in all-night events                   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Tuner: Keep control in Drift and Time Attack events                 |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Open-Wheel: Perfect your racing line at top speed                   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Street: Ramp up the fear factor on tight city circuits              |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Languages: English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Portuguese,     |
  |   Russian, Japanese and Chinese.                                        |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Update Notes: v1.5 (v131072). Firmware 9.0.1 and master key 7.0 are   |
  |   required.                                                             |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Now that GRID Autosport is out on the track, we plan to move it up    |
  |   a gear with some exciting new features. There are two free updates    |
  |   in development:                                                       |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * 2 player split-screen.                                              |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Local wireless multiplayer for up to 8 players.                     |
  |                                                                         |
  |   2nd Update will conclude in 2020.                                     |
